{"tid":819363,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一天算唔算蝗語？","createTime":"2018-09-14T17:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T05:20:52.000Z","uid":199211,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"218762edf7c7207d301c6f1572e12a9456e84ed1","tid":819363,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T17:20:30.000Z","msg":"明明好多古籍都係叫一日 求其舉啲例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.吾日三省吾身<br />\n2.三日不讀書 面目可憎<br />\n3.明日歌<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解小學要教一天 搞到一日好似係廣東話口語咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7d079d1ffbab9ab26bed5262d50b1d11311162","tid":819363,"uid":57677,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"我細細個已經學書面語<br />\n<br />\n一天冇問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你玩鳩我呀"},{"pid":"0a9f9ab606974c7a6a018a92973032b6a0dee7a7","tid":819363,"uid":208726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T17:27:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbcd576061aaf3564b8ce27e70607fb8275cdda7","tid":819363,"uid":65449,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T17:31:53.000Z","msg":"書面語量詞都要俾你屌?"},{"pid":"4f12d31649f9dbe94d541f5e5a92e377f0b4f535","tid":819363,"uid":192491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"岩, 書面語根撚本就係蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ab1168e48e511c7e7f060d0ddd59ef4090c9e1","tid":819363,"uid":130568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T18:09:53.000Z","msg":"棄我去者，昨日之日不可留；亂我心者，今日之日多煩憂"},{"pid":"c55ccae3e8f81cf040fd46b420440298df8ea29e","tid":819363,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3ab1168e48e511c7e7f060d0ddd59ef4090c9e1","tid":819363,"uid":130568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":